text: Twin Falls County is a county in the U.S. state of Idaho. As of the 2020 Census, the county had a population of 90,046. The county seat and largest city is Twin Falls. ==Communities== *Buhl *Castleford *Filer *Hansen *Hollister *Kimberly *Murtaugh *Rogerson *Twin Falls ==References== Category:1907 establishments in the United States Category:1900s establishments in Idaho
